                    <section>
                    	<h1>WTF is node.js ?</h1>
                    	<blockquote class="fragment">The illegitimate child of Google and Netscape !</blockquote>
                    </section>
                    <section>
                    	<img src="img/theory.png" alt="from google" />
                    </section>
                    <section>
                    	<img src="img/theory2.png" alt="from netscape" />
                    </section>
                    <section>
                    	<img src="img/rya.jpg" alt="rya" />
                    	<p>2008, Ryan Dahl</p>
                    	<blockquote>How to build scalable real-time web app with simplicity ?</blockquote>
                    	
                    	<aside class="notes">
	 - 2008: Ryan Dahl needed a new way to build _real-time_ web app (push based), with 2 priorities: scalability and simplicity.
     - Netscape -> JS -> JavaScript the good parts
     - Gmail -> Chome -> V8
     - Non blocking I/O for scalability
     - JS for simplicity
						</aside>
                    </section>
